---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About" description="Learn more about Lars van Blitterswijk">
  <div class="space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
    <div class="profile-section">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-8 mb-6">
        <img 
          src="/img/avatar.jpg" 
          alt="Lars van Blitterswijk" 
          class="w-52 h-52 sm:w-72 sm:h-72 lg:w-80 lg:h-80 rounded-lg object-cover shadow-lg mx-auto sm:mx-0 flex-shrink-0"
        />
        <div class="text-left">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-0">Lars van Blitterswijk</h2>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 -mt-1">Automation, AI & Security Engineering</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bio-section">
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">About Me</h3>
      <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I build AI-driven automation that connects systems and removes manual work.
          My core craft is automation engineering with n8n, designing RAG systems, AI agents,
          and end-to-end workflows that integrate systems across the business.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work spans security and software. I automate the cybersecurity process from threat
          hunting to incident response, and I develop across C#, Python, PowerShell, and Bash,
          grounded in a foundation in information security management.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="interests-section">
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Skills & Expertise</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="interest-card bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200 mb-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
            <i class="fas fa-robot mr-2"></i>
            AI Automation & Agents
          </h4>
          <ul class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>n8n workflow automation</li>
            <li>AI agents and RAG systems</li>
            <li>System integration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="interest-card bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-lg border border-green-100 dark:border-green-800/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-800 dark:text-green-200 mb-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt mr-2"></i>
            Security Automation
          </h4>
          <ul class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Automated threat hunting</li>
            <li>Incident response automation</li>
            <li>Automating cybersecurity processes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="interest-card bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-lg border border-purple-100 dark:border-purple-800/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 mb-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
            <i class="fas fa-code mr-2"></i>
            Software Development
          </h4>
          <ul class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>C#, Python, PowerShell, and Bash</li>
            <li>Custom system integration and APIs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="interest-card bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-lg border border-orange-100 dark:border-orange-800/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-200 mb-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
            <i class="fas fa-lock mr-2"></i>
            Information Security
          </h4>
          <ul class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-300 leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Incident investigation and threat analysis</li>
            <li>Security governance</li>
            <li>Information security management foundation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="interest-card sm:col-span-2 bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-900/20 p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-lg border border-teal-100 dark:border-teal-800/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-teal-800 dark:text-teal-200 mb-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
            <i class="fas fa-users mr-2"></i>
            Agile Way of Working
          </h4>
          <ul class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-teal-700 dark:text-teal-300 leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Scrum Master and Product Owner experience</li>
            <li>Iterative, team-based delivery</li>
            <li>Cross-functional collaboration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-section">
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Get In Touch</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:flex lg:flex-wrap gap-3 sm:gap-4">
        <a 
          href="https://github.com/larsjelle" 
          target="_blank" 
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="contact-link bg-gray-500 bg-opacity-40 text-white no-underline px-4 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-60 transition-all duration-200 text-center sm:text-left touch-manipulation min-h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center sm:justify-start"
        >
          <i class="fab fa-github mr-2 text-base"></i>
          <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">GitHub</span>
        </a>
        
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lars-van-blitterswijk/"
          target="_blank" 
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="contact-link bg-gray-500 bg-opacity-40 text-white no-underline px-4 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-60 transition-all duration-200 text-center sm:text-left touch-manipulation min-h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center sm:justify-start"
        >
          <i class="fab fa-linkedin mr-2 text-base"></i>
          <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">LinkedIn</span>
        </a>
        
        <a 
          href="mailto:contact@larsjelle.nl"
          class="contact-link bg-gray-500 bg-opacity-40 text-white no-underline px-4 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-60 transition-all duration-200 text-center sm:text-left touch-manipulation min-h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center sm:justify-start"
        >
          <i class="fas fa-envelope mr-2 text-base"></i>
          <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">Email</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
